casebody.data:
No. 291,

Misc.

Morales et al. v. City of Galveston et al. Arthur J. Mandell for petitioners. Preston Shirley for the City of Galveston, and Clarence S. Eastham for Cardigan Shipping Co., respondents.

Motion to use the record in No. 167, Misc., October Term, 1960, granted. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit granted. Case transferred to appellate docket.
